<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: You can cure scars with synthetic tissue and glitterworld medicine. Make sure the allowed medicines are correctly set, or the surgeon may not be able to use the required glitterworld medicine on the patient. -->
  <EPOEForkedTips.tips.0>你可以用合成皮肤和闪耀世界药物治疗疤痕。请确保允许使用的药物设置正确，否则手术医生可能无法在病人身上使用所需的闪耀世界药物。</EPOEForkedTips.tips.0>
  <!-- EN: Bad backs and frailty can be cured with neuromuscular framework. You will need the Synthetic Repair research to make them. They require glitterworld medicines, hyperweave and advanced components to manufacture. -->
  <EPOEForkedTips.tips.1>背痛和体弱可以用神经肌肉结构治愈。你将需要先研究并理解人工修复技术作为科技前提，还需要闪耀世界药物、超织品和先进零部件来制造它们。</EPOEForkedTips.tips.1>
  <!-- EN: Dementia and Alzheimers can be cured with neuro-cure framework. You will need the Neurological Treatment research to make them. They require glitterworld medicines, hyperweave, neuromuscular framework and MA-AI chips to manufacture. -->
  <EPOEForkedTips.tips.2>痴呆症和阿尔茨海默症可以用神经治疗结构治愈。你将需要研究并理解神经治疗技术作为科技前提，还需要闪耀世界药物、超织物、神经肌肉结构和医疗助理芯片来制造它们。</EPOEForkedTips.tips.2>
  <!-- EN: Broken scyther blades can be acquired from dismantling Scyther mechanoids. They can be smelted for further plasteel, or restore them into Scyther blades that you can use for other prosthetic items. -->
  <EPOEForkedTips.tips.3>损坏的镰刃可以通过拆解机械飞螳获得。它们可以被熔炼成基础资源，或者修好作为一种义肢替代品。</EPOEForkedTips.tips.3>
  <!-- EN: Organic Optimizers nanobots are a new category of body upgrades. The Instinct Optimizers have unique benefits on different body parts. Body purists are safe to receive them, whilst Transhumanists abhor them. -->
  <EPOEForkedTips.tips.4>机体优化纳米机器人是一种新型的身体升级产品。而超感优化纳米机器人对不同的身体部位有独特的强化方式。身体纯粹主义者可以平静地接受“改造”，而超人类主义者则十分厌恶这种产品的工作方式。</EPOEForkedTips.tips.4>
  <!-- EN: You can have as many different implants you want on a natural body part. Go crazy on installing as many different rib or brain implants on a single colonist! -->
  <EPOEForkedTips.tips.5>可以在同一个身体部位安装多个类似的植入物。比如在一个殖民者身上安上一堆肋骨植入物或者脑部植入物。</EPOEForkedTips.tips.5>
  
</LanguageData>